      "n": 28,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Ka wiꞥſch pahr to ta\nrabbaga Brehfschanu wedd/\nn to Behdigo Kleegfchanu pa-\nlaufs.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 29,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Rad wiꞥſch Meeru dohd/\nas tad apbehdinahs? kad wiꞥſch\no Waigu apflepj/ kas tad wiꞥ-\nu redſehs jeb Tauta jeb Zil-\neks weenlihdsi?\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 30,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Ka tee wiltigi Laudis ne\nvalda / nn teem Laudim par\nWalgeim ne irr.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 31,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Irrag wiꞥſch us to\nto pareist effaim / ka tu fakki:\nMan irr wairak Taifnibas ne ka\ntam STIPRAM DEE-\nWAM?\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 32,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Ja kas irr/ ko es ne ef-\nnu redſeis/to mahzi tu man/ ef-\nnu es Netaifnibu darrijs / tad\ns to ne gribbu wairs darriht.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 33,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Buhs tad ( Deewam )\ndo tewis waizaht / ka tam buhs\ntmaftaht ? jo tu atmetti to\nPahrmahzifchanu/) woj tad\new bij darriht fo gribbefchan /\nn ne man? fo tu nu finnt to\nunna.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 34,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Sirdigi Laudis to pa-\nchu ar mannim fazzihg / un\nveens gudrs Wihrs man klau-\nihs.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 35,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Ijabs irr neprattigi run-\najs/ un winna Wahrdi ne irr\ngudri biſſſchi.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 36,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Mans Tehws/ lat Ijabs\nohp pahrbaudihts lihds Gallam/\napchz ka tas pee netaifneem Lau-\nim greeschahs.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 37,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Jo wiꞥſch pahr taweem\nGrehkeem wehl wairak pahr-\nfahps / zittadi wiꞥſch preekſch\nmuhſahn Azzim Plaukſtes fa-\nsittihs/ un wairohs wehl jawas\nKunnaschanas prett to STIP-\nRU DEEWU.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 1,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "N Elijus atbildēja\nwehl/ nn fazzija:\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 2,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Woj tu fchkeeti\nMan irr wairak Taifnibas ne ka\ntam STIPRAM DEE-\nWAM?\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 3,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Jo tu fakki: Kastew no ta\natlezz? ko tad wairak es eespeh-\nschu (ar mannu Taifnibu /)\nne ka ar manneem Grehkeem.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 4,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Es atbildeschu tew weenu\nWahrdi/un taweem Draugeem\nar tew.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 5,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Skattajs prett Debbeſi un\nraugi/ usluhko tahs Padebbeſis/\nkas irr augstakas ne ka tu.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 6,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Ja tu (prett winnu)\ngrehko / ko warri tu ar winnu\ndarriht: un kad tawu Pahrfahp-\nchanu dauds irr/ ko tu winnam\ndarrifi?\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 7,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Effi tu taifns/ ko warri\ntu winnam doht / jeb ko dabbu\nwiꞥſch no tawas Rohkas.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 8,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Tawa Besdeevisa warre-\ntu prett kahdu Zilweku buht/ ka\ntu effi/ untawa Taifniba preekſch\nkahdu Zilweka Behruu.\n"
    }
  ],
